data.description: This is a must see and great location. Updated windows, a/c, and roof. Easy maintenance front yard, covered back patio, garage and so much more. walk into this light and airy living area with beautiful flooring, bay window with plantation shutters. Enjoy cooking in remodeled kitchen. Backyard with coverd patio and 2 person hot tub perfect to relax in night or day. Spacious master bedroom with walk-in shower, bidet and heated toilet seat in the bathroom.
